[[Image:Yada_Kouji.jpg|thumb|right|K<U+014D>ji Yada]]'''K<U+014D>ji Yada''' ('''<U+77E2><U+7530><U+8015><U+53F8>''', ''Yada Kouji''), born [[April 15]], [[1933]] in [[Tokyo]], is a veteran [[seiyuu]]. He is currently represented by [[Aoni Production]]. K<U+014D>ji Yada is also his birth name, but it is written with different [[kanji]] ('''<U+77E2><U+7530><U+5F18><U+4E8C>''', ''Yada Kouji'').

